<paragraph blockId="0.[151,1436,1555,1910]" pageId="0" pageNumber="597">
<keyLead pageId="0" pageNumber="597">-. Fore ocellus situated about middle of inner margin of compound eyes, ocellar setae III arising just outside ocellar triangle, at least on the outer tangent between fore and hind ocelli; post ocular setae in a straight line far away from eye margin, post ocular setae III not specially developed, almost equal to post ocular setae I; legs brown, except apex of fore tibiae and tarsi yellow; fore tibia without a spine at apex ...................................................................................................................................................................... 2</keyLead>
